Project: Flipkart Sentiment Analysis Using NLP

Description:
A Natural Language Processing project to classify Flipkart customer reviews as positive or negative to understand customer sentiments.

Technologies Used:
Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, NLTK/TextBlob

Features / Highlights:
1.Preprocessed text data: cleaning, tokenization, stopword removal.
2.Converted text to numerical features using TF-IDF vectorization.
3.Trained models: Logistic Regression and Naive Bayes.
4.Built a predictive pipeline to classify new customer reviews.
5.Visualized results using confusion matrices and classification reports.

Outcome:
1.Achieved an overall accuracy of ~87%.
2.Developed a functional real-time sentiment prediction system.
